Arms (Blazon)
Per bend wavy Azure and Gules, a bend wavy Argent between in chief a scallop Or and a stag courant Argent, and in base an anvil Sable.

Crest (Blazon)
On a helm with mantling Azure doubled Vert, a torse of the same, thereon a mullet of eight points Argent.

Motto
Fidèle à ses racines
(“Faithful to one’s roots”)
